OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDrug targets for prisons in
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FEngland and Wales          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Jails in England and Wales will be set 
OL,6, targets for the first time to keep out 
OL,7, drugs under prison reform proposals.   
OL,9,FThe plans in the government White Paper
OL,10,F- proposals for future laws - include  
OL,11,Fassessing every new inmate for drug    
OL,12,Faddiction upon arrival.                
OL,14,FMinisters say the "stringent targets"  
OL,15,Fwill hold prison governors to account. 
OL,17,FThe plan is closely tied to Monday's   
OL,18,Fannouncement of an attempt to "rebuild"
OL,19,Fdrug treatment programmes in England   
OL,20,Fand Wales after years of cuts.         
